1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful,
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:58,820
[Episode 17]

15
00:00:58,820 --> 00:01:01,980
[I will have you share my pain
and witness my joy.]

16
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:04,380
I'm an undercover agent
for the Beizhou government.

17
00:01:04,380 --> 00:01:06,140
I've been ordered
to impersonate the Young Leader

18
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:07,900
and investigate the munition smuggling.

19
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:10,100
Then who

20
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,020
is the real Guzhou?

21
00:01:17,100 --> 00:01:18,300
I'll take care of that.

22
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:21,300
Mohan, let's go.

23
00:01:21,300 --> 00:01:22,220
Have a dance with me.

24
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:29,940
Qinghuan.

25
00:01:32,380 --> 00:01:33,780
You should have got the message.

26
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:36,020
A large batch of munitions
will be shipped in.

27
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:38,380
Since we have the same goal,

28
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:39,540
we can work together.

29
00:01:42,380 --> 00:01:43,580
We've been through a lot.

30
00:01:43,980 --> 00:01:45,100
I trust you.

31
00:01:45,460 --> 00:01:46,860
But the organization behind you...

32
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:49,020
I understand your concerns.

33
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:50,900
But it's now or never.

34
00:01:51,260 --> 00:01:52,620
I got a reliable tip.

35
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:54,500
The shipping details of the munitions

36
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:58,580
are in the briefcase
of the chamber president.

37
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:02,380
We need to get it.

38
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:05,660
I have an idea.

39
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:22,020
How do you find today's arrangements

40
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:24,940
by Joys of Life?

41
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:26,340
You speak Japanese?

42
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:29,740
Miss Yu, you are a surprise indeed.

43
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:32,940
Just a little bit.

44
00:02:33,220 --> 00:02:34,060
I've prepared

45
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:35,100
a hometown song

46
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,500
for you.

47
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:39,100
But my throat is not helping these days.

48
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,220
If I were to perform,

49
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:42,500
I'd only make a fool of myself
in front of you.

50
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:45,020
No wonder everyone in Beizhou says

51
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:46,500
you're quite a character.

52
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:49,140
I wonder if I could have
a dance with you.

53
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:50,700
I'm flattered.

54
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:51,980
It would be my honor.

55
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:55,540
Send it to the private room
and keep a close watch.

56
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:15,300
Drinks, please.

57
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:16,900
Here.

58
00:03:30,860 --> 00:03:31,820
Mohan,

59
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:34,660
if we do it the Chinese way,

60
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:37,540
we should drink this together.

61
00:03:44,940 --> 00:03:45,700
Sorry.

62
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:48,460
I'll take you
to the restroom to clean it up.

63
00:03:48,460 --> 00:03:49,020
Okay.

64
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:03,820
My apologies, sir.

65
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:06,340
I have important matters
to discuss with Miss Yu.

66
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:12,220
Let go of me. We're in public.

67
00:04:12,220 --> 00:04:13,580
Do you want to make a scene here?

68
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:15,180
Go with me
if you don't want a big scene.

69
00:04:15,820 --> 00:04:16,700
Or I don't know

70
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:18,220
what I will do.

71
00:04:26,380 --> 00:04:28,060
What were you planning with Chu Yunfan?

72
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:29,900
I was just catching up
with my old friend.

73
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:31,300
What are you worried about?

74
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:33,780
The whole Joys of Life

75
00:04:33,780 --> 00:04:35,900
is being closely guarded
by the Marshal's people.

76
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:37,860
Do not do anything.

77
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:39,180
Tonight,

78
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:41,660
just be good and stay by my side.

79
00:04:44,700 --> 00:04:45,780
Then,

80
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,380
in what capacity

81
00:04:47,380 --> 00:04:48,700
do I stay by your side?

82
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:53,540
It's a good day
for you and Miss Chihoko.

83
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:58,900
You know

84
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:01,860
this isn't what I truly want.

85
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:02,820
I know even better

86
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:04,780
what you have done

87
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:06,100
to get where you are now,

88
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:07,420
sir.

89
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:11,660
Miss Yu,

90
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:13,860
you're fluttering around
like a butterfly today.

91
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:17,020
First, you were flirting with Mr. Chu.

92
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:19,580
Then you were attentive

93
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:21,020
to my father.

94
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:25,500
And now,

95
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:28,380
are you after my fiancé?

96
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,740
Miss Chihoko,

97
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,860
you'd better keep a close eye
on your fiancé

98
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:37,660
lest I take him away.

99
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:39,100
What did you say?

100
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:43,540
It's not nice to get angry
on such a happy day.

101
00:05:44,540 --> 00:05:46,540
Qinghuan, don't be naughty.

102
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:55,660
Right.

103
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:58,780
With a good man like Mr. Chu
by your side,

104
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:02,020
you should be content, right?

105
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:08,100
Am I right, Mohan?

106
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:14,380
Mohan,

107
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:17,460
I'm a bit drunk.

108
00:06:17,980 --> 00:06:19,980
Take me back
to the private room for rest.

109
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:25,900
Don't play with fire.

110
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:37,620
The briefcase is
in Room Moon in Flowers.

111
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:40,260
Your people are trying
to distract the guards.

112
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:42,300
Okay.

113
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,740
You wait in the hall
to create a distraction

114
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:45,740
and cover for me.

115
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:46,260
Mhm.

116
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:53,580
Let's go there.

117
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:54,940
Let's go there too.

118
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:55,740
Sir.

119
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:57,780
Sir, you are an impressive drinker.

120
00:06:57,780 --> 00:06:58,460
Of course.

121
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:27,220
[Munition Shipment List]
[Military Secret Order]

122
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:01,540
What are you doing here?

123
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:04,900
I was going to perform
a song for the president.

124
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:06,900
I'm bringing some tea
for him to sober up.

125
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,500
Strange I don't see him.

126
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,860
Where is he?

127
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:11,580
Really?

128
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:14,140
I hope you're not up to something else.

129
00:08:15,260 --> 00:08:18,260
Look what's talking.

130
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:20,260
You looked like a thief.

131
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:21,460
I'm not a thief.

132
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:23,740
I'm here to catch one.

133
00:08:37,260 --> 00:08:38,420
Mohan.

134
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:40,620
Jiang Mohan.

135
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:50,460
You're here.

136
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:53,780
I've been looking for you.

137
00:08:58,700 --> 00:08:59,700
You're drunk.

138
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:02,020
Let me get you tea to sober up.

139
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:30,580
Mohan.

140
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,740
You are

141
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:35,580
so nice to me.

142
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:38,740
That's a bit too coincidental.

143
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:40,780
Is he here looking for the files too?

144
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,940
Does he have another identity?

145
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:45,220
Is he Guzhou?

146
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:47,420
No, no way.

147
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,020
No matter what,

148
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:50,580
let me get the message out.

149
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:52,220
I can test him later.

150
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,740
You shameless woman.

151
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:28,900
How dare you have an affair
with my man?

152
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,300
If you don't know how to talk,

153
00:10:31,540 --> 00:10:33,180
I don't mind helping shut your mouth.

154
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:48,340
Chihoko,

155
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:50,060
enough!

156
00:10:52,700 --> 00:10:53,500
Go.

157
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,820
Yu Qinghuan,

158
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:16,220
you'll be so sorry very soon.

159
00:11:32,460 --> 00:11:36,180
♪The waves♪

160
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:40,460
♪When will you stop
looking through them?♪

161
00:11:40,540 --> 00:11:44,500
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

162
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:48,660
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

163
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:51,420
♪I thought you were an angel♪

164
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:53,700
♪An angel who watched over me♪

165
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:56,780
♪And saw every side of me♪

166
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:59,420
♪Until reality is flooded♪

167
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:01,660
♪You become sensible♪

168
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:06,220
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

169
00:12:06,540 --> 00:12:09,060
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

170
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:11,100
♪All clamoring because of you♪

171
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:13,180
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

172
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:15,620
♪I cannot hear you♪

173
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:19,140
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

174
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:22,660
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

175
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,980
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

176
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:27,140
♪And thought there was ample time♪

177
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:29,180
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

178
00:12:29,300 --> 00:12:31,260
♪But you always make me panic♪

179
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:35,580
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

180
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:38,940
♪How much I am worth♪
